## Validation Queries

> **Note:** Replace the following placeholders before running:
> - `{TABLE}` = consume table name (e.g., `usage_nonvee.reading_ivl_nonvee_oh`)
> - `{UPDATE_USER_FILTER}` = `('info-insert', 'info-update')` for Info/LG pipelines, `('auth-insert', 'auth-update')` for Auth pipeline
