### Query 1: Get Latest Run Timestamp

**Purpose:** Identify the most recent run for the target usage date.

```sql
SELECT 
    hdp_update_user,
    MAX(hdp_insert_dttm) AS latest_insert_ts,
    MAX(hdp_update_dttm) AS latest_update_ts,
    CAST(MAX(hdp_insert_dttm) AS DATE) AS latest_run_dt,
    COUNT(*) AS total_rows
FROM {TABLE}
WHERE hdp_update_user IN {UPDATE_USER_FILTER}
  AND aep_usage_dt = '{USAGE_DATE}'
GROUP BY hdp_update_user;
```

