### Query 2: Total Record Count — Insert vs Update

**Purpose:** Compare overall volume between DEV and PROD.

```sql
SELECT 
    hdp_update_user,
    COUNT(*) AS total_rows,
    COUNT(DISTINCT serialnumber) AS dist_meters,
    COUNT(DISTINCT aep_channel_id) AS dist_channels,
    COUNT(DISTINCT aep_raw_uom) AS dist_uom,
    COUNT(DISTINCT aep_premise_nb) AS dist_premises,
    MIN(starttimeperiod) AS min_starttime,
    MAX(endtimeperiod) AS max_endtime,
    MIN(hdp_insert_dttm) AS min_insert_ts,
    MAX(hdp_insert_dttm) AS max_insert_ts
FROM {TABLE}
WHERE hdp_update_user IN {UPDATE_USER_FILTER}
  AND aep_usage_dt = '{USAGE_DATE}'
  AND hdp_insert_dttm >= CAST('{LATEST_RUN_DT}' AS DATE)
GROUP BY hdp_update_user;
```

