### Query 5: starttime/endtime Calculation Validation

**Purpose:** Verify `endtime - starttime = aep_sec_per_intrvl` (IntervalLength * 60).

```sql
SELECT 
    hdp_update_user,
    COUNT(*) AS total,
    SUM(CASE 
        WHEN (unix_timestamp(substr(endtimeperiod, 1, 19), 'yyyy-MM-dd''T''HH:mm:ss') 
            - unix_timestamp(substr(starttimeperiod, 1, 19), 'yyyy-MM-dd''T''HH:mm:ss')) 
            = CAST(aep_sec_per_intrvl AS INTEGER)
        THEN 1 ELSE 0 
    END) AS time_calc_PASS,
    SUM(CASE 
        WHEN (unix_timestamp(substr(endtimeperiod, 1, 19), 'yyyy-MM-dd''T''HH:mm:ss') 
            - unix_timestamp(substr(starttimeperiod, 1, 19), 'yyyy-MM-dd''T''HH:mm:ss')) 
            != CAST(aep_sec_per_intrvl AS INTEGER)
        THEN 1 ELSE 0 
    END) AS time_calc_FAIL
FROM {TABLE}
WHERE hdp_update_user IN {UPDATE_USER_FILTER}
  AND aep_usage_dt = '{USAGE_DATE}'
  AND hdp_insert_dttm >= CAST('{LATEST_RUN_DT}' AS DATE)
GROUP BY hdp_update_user;
```

