## Validation Execution Checklist

### Per Pipeline (Info / Auth / LG), Per OpCo:

| Step | Query | DEV | PROD | Match? |
|------|-------|-----|------|--------|
| 1 | Q1: Get latest run timestamp | | | |
| 2 | Q2: Total record count | | | |
| 3 | Q3: Full column NULL profile | | | |
| 4 | Q4: Distinct values / constants | | | |
| 5 | Q5: starttime/endtime math | | | |
| 6 | Q6: MACS join match rate | | | |
| 7 | Q7: MACS sub-column NULLs | | | |
| 8 | Q8: Failed MACS meters | | | |
| 9 | Q9: aep_service_point logic | | | |
| 10 | Q10: Value/scalar validation | | | |
| 11 | Q11: aep_endtime_utc check | | | |
| 12 | Q12: DEV vs PROD count comparison | | | |
| 13 | Q13: Serial number drill-down | | | |
| 14 | Q14: Full data CSV extract + compare | | | |

### Validation Pass Criteria

- Q2: `total_rows` in DEV = `total_rows` in PROD (for same hdp_update_user)
- Q3: NULL counts match between DEV and PROD
- Q5: `time_calc_FAIL` = 0
- Q6: MACS match rate in DEV >= MACS match rate in PROD
- Q9: `ALL_PRESENT` -> `svc_point_null` = 0; `HAS_NULL` -> `svc_point_populated` = 0
- Q10: `sum_value` in DEV = `sum_value` in PROD
- Q12: All metrics match between DEV and PROD
- Q14: CSV diff shows zero differences (excluding `hdp_insert_dttm`, `hdp_update_dttm`)

